title: Jack Ma in Malaysia - DFTZ Digital Free Trade Zone Launch
description: World's 1st Digital Free Trade Zone is the first of its kind out of China. DFTZ was launched by Jack Ma Alibaba in KL Malaysia on 22 March 2017. 28Mall.com CEO Fione Tan was invited as guest to this event and look forward to help SMEs and biz owners start their cross border ecommerce between Asean and China. COntact www.eOneNet.com or www.28Mall.com
